  "texts": [
    "This step involved extracting the plain text content and relevant header information from the emails, while discarding any attachments to simplify the initial analysis framework.",
    "2) Normalization: The text data underwent normalization to reduce complexity.",
    "This included converting all characters to lowercase and removing special characters and numbers, which helps in standardizing the text data for analysis.",
    "3) Tokenization: The normalized text was then tokenized, splitting the text into individual words or tokens.",
    "This facilitates the analysis of language usage patterns and the frequency of specific words within the dataset.4) Removing Stop Words: Commonly used words that carry minimal informational content, known as stop words, were removed from the text."
  ]
}